[[File:CloneTrooperGrenadier-SWM.jpg|thumb|right|250px|A [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone trooper]] grenadier.]]
'''Clone trooper grenadiers''' were [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] developed to offer concentrated firepower to the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] using [[Grenade/Legends|grenades]].<ref name="GB:GAotR">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20050324b|text=Grand Army of the Republic}}</ref> Another favored weapon of the grenadiers were [[Grenade launcher/Legends|grenade launchers]].<ref name="BFI">''[[Star Wars: Battlefront]]''</ref> In typical patrols, the ratio of regular [[Cloning/Legends|clone]] troopers to clone [[Trooper/Legends|trooper]] grenadiers was roughly three to one.<ref name="GB:GAotR" /> Once deployed clone grenadiers would devastate close combat battles. They often used [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonators]] to destroy vehicles and enemy outposts.<ref name="GB:CC">''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds: Clone Campaigns]]''</ref>

==Variations==
*'''Thermal Detonator Trooper:''' These troopers used [[Mortar/Legends|mortars]] to shoot [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonators]]. They fought alongside [[General/Legends|General]] [[Echuu Shen-Jon]] during the [[Hunt for the Decimator|Decimator campaign]].<ref name="GB:CC" />
*'[[Clone jet trooper/Legends|''Clone jet trooper]]:''' These aerial clone troopers were known to often use [[Electromagnetic pulse launcher|EMP grenade launchers]].<ref name="BFI" />

